lead_paragraph: With a 25-foot putt from the fringe on the final hole, Morgan Pressel grabbed a share of the lead yesterday in the Safeway Classic at Portland, Ore. Pressel shot a 69. She joined Jenna Daniels, Jeong Jang and Candie Kung in first place at seven-under-par.
